   
1. Users enter users' name
2. Users enter password
3. Check for length
    3.1 Password 8 characters
        3.1.1 Accept the password if it meets the requirements
    3.2 Password is not 8 characters
        3.2.1 Display message (requirement for the password length)
4. Check for password special characters
    4.1 Password 1 special character
        4.1.1 Accept the password
    4.2 Does not have the special character
        4.2.1 Display message
5. Password verified and meet the requirement => add users in the list